OL,3,CSnow and ice weather warning issued
OL,4,Cfor Wales
OL,6,FThe Met Office has issued a snow and
OL,7,Fice weather warning for Wales this
OL,8,Fweekend, with up to 30cm of snow
OL,9,Fforecast on higher ground.
OL,11,FThe yellow weather warning kicks in at
OL,12,Fnoon on Saturday, 4 January, and lasts
OL,13,Funtil 11.59pm on Sunday, 5 January,
OL,14,Fwith the forecaster warning of some
OL,15,Fdisruption due to "heavy snow, and
OL,16,Fsome freezing rain in places".
OL,18,FIt covers all of Wales and the
OL,19,Fmajority of England.
