OL,3,CSnow and ice weather warning issued
OL,4,Cfor Wales
OL,6,FA three-day weather warning was
OL,7,Finitially in place for snow, but this
OL,8,Fhas been updated to cover snow and ice
OL,9,Fand end on Sunday instead of Monday.
OL,11,FThe forecaster warns that rural
OL,12,Fcommunities could be cut off, while
OL,13,Fpower cuts and travel disruption may
OL,14,Foccur.
