OL,3,CSnow and ice weather warning issued
OL,4,Cfor Wales
OL,6,FThe Met Office warning said: "Some
OL,7,Fsignificant accumulations of snow are
OL,8,Fpossible across parts of Wales, the
OL,9,FMidlands and northern England in
OL,10,Fparticular, at least for a time, where
OL,11,F5cm or more could accumulate fairly
OL,12,Fwidely, with perhaps as much as 20-
OL,13,F30cm over high ground of mid and north
OL,14,FWales and potentially 30-40cm over
OL,15,Fparts of the Pennines. This,
OL,16,Faccompanied by strengthening winds,
OL,17,Fmay lead to drifting of lying snow.
