OL,3,CSnow and ice weather warning issued
OL,4,Cfor Wales
OL,6,F"In addition, as milder air moves
OL,7,Fnorthwards, snow may turn to a spell
OL,8,Fof freezing rain for a time, again
OL,9,Fmore especially across parts of Wales,
OL,10,Fthe Midlands and northern England,
OL,11,Fadding to the risk of ice and leading
OL,12,Fto some treacherous conditions in
OL,13,Fplaces. A fairly rapid thaw of lying
OL,14,Fsnow is possible later on Sunday,
OL,15,Falthough exactly how far north the
OL,16,Frapid thaw will reach remains
OL,17,Funcertain at this stage."
