OL,3,CSnow and ice weather warning issued
OL,4,Cfor Wales
OL,6,FMet Office meteorologist Tom Morgan
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's definitely going to start
OL,8,Foff as snow in many places but it's a
OL,9,Fquestion of how quickly that snow
OL,10,Fmelts and turns back to rain, it's
OL,11,Fmore likely that the snow won't last
OL,12,Fthat long in southern England.
OL,14,F"It's quite likely the warning will be
OL,15,Fupdated quite frequently between now
OL,16,Fand the weekend.
OL,18,F"Certainly if you've got travel plans
OL,19,Fon Sunday and perhaps Monday stay
OL,20,Ftuned into the forecast."
